## MCP Integration

This agent exposes the following MCP tools:

### Tools

| Tool | Input Schema | Output | Description |
|------|-------------|--------|-------------|
| `process` | `z.object({ input: z.string() })` | `{ result: string }` | Main processing endpoint |

### Example Request

```json
{
  "name": "process",
  "arguments": {
    "input": "example input"
  }
}
```

### Example Response

```json
{
  "result": "processed output"
}
```

